:Totahtziné in ilhuicac
:timoyetzticah mā yēctēnēhualo in motocātzin. 
:Mā huāllāuh in motlatocāyōtzin. 
:Mā chīhualo in tlālticpac in ticmonequiltia in iuh 
:chīhualo in ilhuicac. 
:In totlaxcal in momoztlahé totēchmonequi mā āxcān xitēchmomaquili. 
:Mā xitēchmopohpolhuili in totlatlacōl in iuh 
:tiquimpohpolhuia in techtlatlacalhuia. 
:Macāhmo xitēchmotlalcahuili inic ahmo ipan tihuetzque in
:teneyeyecōltiliztli. 
:Mā xitēchmomaquixtili in ihuicpa in ahmo cualli. 
:Mā iuh mochīhua.


